deleteNotchFill(25.10)                                  deleteNotchFill(25.10)

Name
       deleteNotchFill  -  Deletes  all  gaps, notches, acute angles, and hole
       geometries that were inserted by the fillNotch command

Syntax
       deleteNotchFill

       Deletes all gaps, notches, acute angles, and hole geometries that  were
       inserted  by  the fillNotch command. Also deletes geometry with + SHAPE
       DRCFILL in DEF.

              * A gap is a minimum spacing violation.

              * A notch is a minimum step violation.

              *

                An acute angle is a 45 degree violation.

              * A hole is a minimum enclosed area violation.

Parameters
       None

Related Information
              * fillNotch

              * ECO Flows chapter in the Innovus User Guide

